{"type": "article", "id": 5659, "title": "无线工作灯 M Lamp", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-29T08:06:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052338270tyXUqrK8HCPZu9g.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自英国的设计师 David Irwin 为美国制造商 Juniper 设计了一款无线工作灯 M Lamp。David Irwin 的设计灵感来源于 19 世纪矿工的油灯。这款工作等内置了充电电池，可以方便用户带着灯四处行走，简洁的造型摆放在室内也不显得突兀。灯罩的方向可以任意转动，上方的触控板可改变灯光的强弱，为用户提供可移动、可调整且稳定的平光源。之前 M Lamp 还被英国生活类杂志 Living North 评为最佳室内产品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233825oBp6OlCfKdnxH5UZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233825S4D3lcetnkjw7g2V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7984375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233826bBp3GODijfx9Ychm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233826YaiCFGW39nsDQtSe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233826jrZGCUdTDQ7fFx5h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.2\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}